snippet.title: Manifold Garden - Announcement Teaser Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Manifold Garden (previously known as Relativity) is a game that reimagines the rules of the universe http://manifoldgarden.com


Experience infinity in a universe that repeats endlessly in every direction. Explore, discover, then master new rules of physics. 

In this world, falling down leads you back to the top. Up is down and down is up. 

http://manifoldgarden.com/
